{"tid":427771,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"長文慎入 阿元來了食晚餐趣聞","createTime":"2017-10-07T15:43:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-07T15:57:22.000Z","uid":139376,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"12c75caea8629e521ef598b1da28a6f7e867333d","tid":427771,"uid":139376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T15:43:41.000Z","msg":"是咁的，頭先同女友去左觀塘阿元來了食晚餐，咁<br />\n<br />\n就同左1pair望落好曖昧嘅男女朋友搭枱，以下係佢<br />\n<br />\n地嘅對話。<br />\n<br />\n男:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n女:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(用手托住個下巴望住個男仔) : 我呢，媽咪10月中<br />\n<br />\n去韓國旅行，你可唔可以陪我呀？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 咁姐係幾時呀？10月11同10月20都係月中<br />\n<br />\n喎！你俾個明確時間俾我考慮下先啦，要睇下我<br />\n<br />\nSchedule有冇時間先得架嘛！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 好啦咁，咁去露營好唔好？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 咁你姐係玩鳩我姐！去露營要帶營架嘛，<br />\n<br />\n咪姐係要我帶曬啲野？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (打一打男仔個膊頭): 唔係玩鳩你呀！我識煮野食<br />\n<br />\n架！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 咁我帶營啦，你煮野食啦！不過我都煮得<br />\n<br />\n好叻<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :係咩！(又打一打個男仔)<br />\n<br />\n之後又轉左話題<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 咁你有冇女朋友呀？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 我架單車就係我老婆<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 咁你攬住佢訓就得啦，hahahaha<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 係呀，佢係我間房黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : (不停係度傻笑)<br />\n<br />\n記憶中淨係記到咁多，我同女朋友食完晚餐之後係<br />\n<br />\n咁討論你地，其他人唔知仲以為你地先係情侶，我<br />\n<br />\n地只不過係搭枱嘅路人，你地真係好sweet<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，快啲拍拖啦好嗎？<br />\n<br />\n目測戴帽嘅男仔應該係好仔，而女仔都好lum你下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，如果你地睇到呢個post，希望你地是但<br />\n<br />\n一個快啲action，好好享受拍拖嘅樂趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我係白色衫同你地搭枱個條仔"},{"pid":"efa29b26d51e84c288ca3d7a4e5f55f793d4664f","tid":427771,"uid":139376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T15:48:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"531cdd19e824f373a6a8a42ff009a613f7338a89","tid":427771,"uid":139376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T15:53:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1269db8797af1876d2ec4018ca28af8a0886e82d","tid":427771,"uid":29093,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T15:55:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">果然係 痴痴呆呆 坐埋一枱 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n樓主喺度不停傻笑"},{"pid":"fedf716565d0f6c6a0ca7151d881bb9d6faa11c2","tid":427771,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T15:57:22.000Z","msg":"唔好拎弱智人士開玩笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}